title: [Vornavian Coast, Coastal Woods]
description: A pair of nocturnal birds flit back and forth among the trees, trilling loudly as they chase one and other through the branches.  High above, the treetops sway in the wind which, while strong up above the trees, slows to a slight breeze on the forest floor.
